"use client" import { Link, useNavigate } from "react-router-dom" import { useAuth } from "../contexts/AuthContext" import { useState } from "react" function Navbar() { const { currentUser, logout } = useAuth() const navigate = useNavigate() const [isOpen, setIsOpen] = useState(false) const handleLogout = () => { logout() navigate("/login") } return (
UK University Finder
{currentUser ? (
setIsOpen(true)} onMouseLeave={() => setIsOpen(false)}>
{isOpen && (
{currentUser.email}
Profile Bookmarks
)}
) : (
Login Register
)}
) } export default Navbar
